	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">要了解全球生活方式，信息图也是一个重要的参考</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-04-25 17:18:06 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">2</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">39</span>
